Class DefaultDesireBindingFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.grouplens.grapht.solver.DefaultDesireBindingFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BindingFunction

    public class DefaultDesireBindingFunction
extends Object
implements BindingFunction
    A binding function that looks for DefaultImplementation or DefaultProvider on the desired type or the qualifier. For constants, it will also check for DefaultDouble, DefaultInteger, DefaultBoolean, and DefaultString.
